name: ACEToken
description:
Ground-breaking altcoin ACEToken bridges the everyday commercial business model with the crypto economy. Built on the Binance smart chain with 1 trillion fixed total circulating supply.
ACEToken is a token that provides revenue through everyday business modelling with aims to revolutionize the decentralized finance industry by building its unique supply chain for personal protective equipment (PPE). Additionally, ACE will invest in green energy projects.
ACE intends to contribute 50% of the profits from PPE sales and dividends from investments to the liquidity pool, ensuring ACEToken price growth.
